{"tid":1945220,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"5廠商獲資助月供政府1000萬口罩  僅2萬個流入市場","createTime":"2020-03-27T02:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T02:47:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b4f4736e116a73a6885ae8d88f5cdc726f144466","tid":1945220,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:12:36.000Z","msg":"商務及經濟發展局今日公布，在本地口罩生產資助計畫下多批出5宗申請，當中共涉及6條生產線。6條生產線預計投產後，每月共可為政府提供約1000萬個口罩，另有2萬個供應本地市場。<br />\n<br />\n連同上星期批出的兩條生產線，計畫已批出8條生產線。計畫最多會資助20條本地生產線，目前尚有12條生產線資助名額。由於預計符合資格的生產線數目很有可能已超越餘下的資助名額，有關計關今日起停止接受申請。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1733112/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-5%E5%BB%A0%E5%95%86%E7%8D%B2%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E6%9C%88%E4%BE%9B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C1000%E8%90%AC%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-2%E8%90%AC%E5%80%8B%E6%B5%81%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4</code></pre>"},{"pid":"4ff029f9ac7a107e144e5b1787d0e97a14e042c7","tid":1945220,"uid":18251,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:13:15.000Z","msg":"去晒民賤聯道？"},{"pid":"309f8e393d2854e559770bea1a1554e894a8f506","tid":1945220,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:13:18.000Z","msg":"同市民搶口罩"},{"pid":"6cd4a90c12e5f5f49df5a360f9ee05443fa7db8f","tid":1945220,"uid":3513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:15:12.000Z","msg":"1000萬個俾政府 幾多個落到市民手？<br />\n又拎資源幫建制做選舉工程？？"},{"pid":"ee7052eb7c7427f1de8aaeacb59b7684cc425047","tid":1945220,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:15:45.000Z","msg":"去晒中國"},{"pid":"2c4cb9c76caa5806a55f1b00f9bde9cb2465f5ff","tid":1945220,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:15:54.000Z","msg":"仆街共匪政府！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"